Original art by @nicosbighead !
Debuted the Grinch at HolMat this year! So dang fun!

Merry Christmas...even Whoville i GUESS 💚
Last weekend at @holidaymatsuri was so fun like....i had a absolute blast. It really felt like conventions were back in full swing!
I got to debut my cosplay based on the amazing art by @nicosbighead ! I saw her design last year and fell in 100% love it i absolutely had to make it!

It felt like the Panini really took a lot of motivation from me to post. Getting to see everyone and them twlling me thwy missed my regular posts was just the push i needed to get motivation back!
I thrive on interactions when i post. It lets me know people actually see what im doing so i REALLY appreciate everyone who comments like...really thank you! 

Costume, hair and makeup by me!

#HolidayMatsuri #holmat #GrinchCosplay #NicosBigHead #Cosplay

Make sure to check out their schedule to see the lineup of programming we got going!

Happy #blackfaeday everyone 🧚‍♀️💙

You know what's crazy? Growing up I've always went exploring in the gardens behind my local Art Museum while my sisters were at the library across the street.
I'd collect the shiny rocks washed up from the creek and hide them in a Tree knot for when I returned. 
Feeling like a Magical little woodland fairy never really ended for me 💕

🧚‍♀️:Wing overlay by @fancyfairyangela 
🧚‍♀️: Event by @blackfaedayofficial 
📷: by Me !

Its an honor to be a returning Guest for @momocon for 2023 and we have a lot to show this weekend!

[I've made a schedule so you cant miss me!]

This year im on the judges panel alongside other talented professionals to judge the costume contest all weekend as well as attending my booth (Cosplay Aisle #117) for meet and Greets in between!
On Sunday im doing a panel with @storytellercosplay & @yayahan on Diversiry Support in Cosplay!

Im very excited to see everyones entries this year as its the biggest Costume Contest around! (Im spoiled, i get to see HOURS of contestants and i will try not to Fangirl over you)

See you this weekend!

📷: by the TALENTED @solitadphoto as always!

Thats a WRAP @momocon 2023!
What a jammed packed convention im so happy to have met you all this weekend and you made it so magical!
I got to debut my Miruko Cosplay and it was well recieved so thank you for making me feel PLUS ULTRA!
Our booth had a line so i really appreciate your patience as well 🙏🏼

The Costume Contest was a major success and im so inspired by everyone who entered! If you competed and have any questions feel free to email me and i would be happy to chop shop! 

Our Diversity panel went very well and sorry we all cried (it was an emotional topic okay? 😅) 

Our 5:00 Press Interview was so fun thank you for all of ypur questions and allowing me time to answer! I wish we could have answered them all so i appreciate you scheduling time!

Lastly thank you to @momocon
And @theloveofthemoon
For having me out this year. It was a BLAST.

(Now....i sleep)

Had the Liberty to snap a few videos of the @momocon Cosplay Craftsmanship Contest! Thank you to EVERYONE who enetered (all 120 of you) and congrats to the winners! ❤️

Thank you @sunlightofastora for the Crowd Footage!

Color Wheel Artist Challenege but Cosplay Edition! 
I saw @nipahcos start this using his cosplays instead of illustrations and i had to join in!

I made sure to tag every talemted artist who helped me by photographing!
Its so cool to see where a image will fall on the colorwheel!

Color theory was my favorite aspect while i was getting my BFA in fine arts and im so happy to combine the two into one image!

This post was SUPER fun to make!

#colorwheel #colorwheelchallenge
